## Third-Party Tools

This pipeline integrates the following open-source bioinformatics tools:

- Prokka (Torsten Seemann, GPL v3)
- MLST (Torsten Seemann, GPL v2)
- Kleborate (Kathryn Holt lab, GPL v3)
- AMRFinder (NCBI, Public Domain)
- Snippy (Torsten Seemann, GPL v2)
- Gubbins (Wellcome Sanger Institute, GPL v2)
- IQ-TREE (Lam-Tung Nguyen et al., BSD License)
- Roary (Andrew J. Page et al., GPL v3)

Please refer to each tool's documentation for full license terms.
